NetworkManager-vpn: NetworkManager-vpn (NetworkManager VPN Plugins)
NetworkManager-vpn:
NetworkManager-vpn: NetworkManager attempts to make networking invisible. When moving 
NetworkManager-vpn: into areas you've been before, NetworkManager automatically connects 
NetworkManager-vpn: to the last network the user chose to connect to. Likewise, when 
NetworkManager-vpn: back at the desk, NetworkManager will switch to the faster, more 
NetworkManager-vpn: reliable wired network connection. 
NetworkManager-vpn:
NetworkManager-vpn: This package contains vpn plugins for NetworkManager to allow easy
NetworkManager-vpn: access to OpenVPN, PPTP, and Vpnc private networks.
NetworkManager-vpn:
